We asked and you delivered! Here are our favorite mac hack submissions. 😋

👉Chicken BBQ: We recommend a rotisserie chicken and your fav BBQ sauce. From @j.o.r.d.n 
👉Extra Cheesy: Mix in a small handful mozzarella for a gooey cheese pull! From @alana_iguana 
👉Nutritional Yeast: Mix a ¼ cup into your cheese, adds a little extra nutrients and a whole lot of flavor. From @miss_valerie_m 
👉Extra Veggie Boost: Grab some broccoli, peas, carrots, or bell peppers and puree those veggies for the picky eater in your fam! From @mustsformamas
